Correlation between two numerical features

train_num <- dplyr::select_if(train, is.numeric)
res <- cor(train_num)
corrplot.mixed(
          res,
          upper="circle",
          lower="number",
          tl.col = "black",
          number.cex = .8,
          tl.cex=.8)
